text: María Montenegro (born 17 September 2000) is a Panamanian international footballer who plays as a defender for the Panama women's national football team. She appeared in two matches for Panama at the 2018 CONCACAF Women's Championship. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Panamanian women's footballers Category:Panama women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders
